---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout title="Privacy Policy — Chitti" description="Learn how Chitti protects your privacy and handles your data with care.">

  <section class="py-24 sm:py-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-text-light">Last updated: March 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-policy mt-12 space-y-10">

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Our Privacy Promise</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            Chitti is built with privacy at its core. We believe your appearance data is deeply personal, and we treat it that way. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, share, and protect your personal information when you use the Chitti mobile application and related services (collectively, the "Service").
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            By using the Service, you agree to the collection and use of information in accordance with this policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We collect only what is necessary to provide and improve our Service:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Account information:</strong> Phone number (for authentication), display name, and region preference.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Photos and images:</strong> Photos you submit for skin or hair analysis. These are processed in real-time and are <strong class="text-text">not permanently stored</strong> on our servers. We use short-lived, time-expiring URLs for image processing — no raw image data is retained after analysis is complete.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Conversation history:</strong> Your chat interactions with AI specialists, stored securely so you can revisit past feedback and recommendations.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Product data:</strong> Products you add to your collection (name, type, routine slot) to personalise recommendations.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Preferences:</strong> Tone preference, persona selection, and context choices used to tailor your experience.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Usage data:</strong> Metadata such as timestamps, analysis type, and interaction patterns. No images or personally identifiable content appear in our logs or analytics.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We use the information we collect to:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Provide, operate, and maintain the Service, including AI-powered skin and hair analysis.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Personalise your experience and deliver tailored beauty recommendations.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Authenticate your identity and secure your account.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Improve and develop new features based on aggregated, de-identified usage patterns.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span>Communicate with you about service updates, security notices, and support.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Third-Party Service Providers</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We work with trusted third-party service providers to deliver and support the Service. These providers are contractually bound to use your data only for the purposes we specify and in accordance with this Privacy Policy. They include:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Cloud infrastructure and database providers</strong> — for secure data storage and authentication with industry-standard access controls.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">AI and machine learning providers</strong> — for processing photos and generating personalised analysis and recommendations. Photos submitted for analysis may be transmitted to these providers for processing; however, they are not used to train third-party AI models.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Analytics providers</strong> — for understanding aggregated usage patterns to improve the Service. No personally identifiable information is shared for analytics purposes.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to any third party for marketing or advertising purposes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We take the security of your data seriously and implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect it:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>All data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.3) and at rest.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Database access is restricted using row-level security policies, ensuring your data is accessible only to you.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>Image processing uses time-expiring signed URLs. Our backend does not store or proxy raw image data.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#10003;</span>
              <span>We regularly review our security practices and update them as necessary to address emerging threats.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            While we strive to protect your personal information, no method of transmission or storage is completely secure. We cannot guarantee absolute security but are committed to maintaining industry-standard protections.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Data Retention</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We retain your personal information only for as long as necessary to fulfil the purposes described in this policy or as required by applicable law. Photos submitted for analysis are processed in real-time and are not retained after the analysis is complete. Account data, conversation history, and preferences are retained for the duration of your account.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Your Rights and Choices</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            You have the following rights regarding your personal information:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-text-light">
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Access and correction:</strong> You can access and update your profile information within the app at any time.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Data deletion:</strong> You may request deletion of your account and all associated data by contacting us at <a href="mailto:privacy@chitti.me" class="font-medium text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">privacy@chitti.me</a>. Upon receiving your request, we will permanently delete your profile, conversations, product data, and preferences within 30 days. This action is irreversible.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex gap-2">
              <span class="mt-1 text-primary">&#8226;</span>
              <span><strong class="text-text">Withdraw consent:</strong> You may stop using the Service at any time. Where we rely on your consent to process data, you may withdraw it by contacting us.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            To exercise any of these rights, please contact us using the details provided below.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            The Service is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If we become aware that we have collected personal information from a child under 13, we will take steps to delete that information promptly.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. When we make changes, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top of this page. We encourage you to review this policy periodically. Continued use of the Service after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-text-light">
            If you have any questions, concerns, or requests regarding this Privacy Policy or our data practices, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@chitti.me" class="font-medium text-primary underline decoration-primary/30 hover:decoration-primary">privacy@chitti.me</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
